httpy Results:

    Average request time: 0.003293 seconds
    95th percentile request time: 0.004315 seconds
  Simple JSON:
    Average request time: 0.003215 seconds
    95th percentile request time: 0.004167 seconds
  Large JSON:
    Average request time: 0.003239 seconds
    95th percentile request time: 0.004179 seconds
  Path Params (1):
    Average request time: 0.003433 seconds
    95th percentile request time: 0.004562 seconds
  Path Params (2):
    Average request time: 0.003442 seconds
    95th percentile request time: 0.004497 seconds
  POST Echo:
    Average request time: 0.003461 seconds
    95th percentile request time: 0.004462 seconds
Average memory usage: 37.24 MB
Average CPU usage: 25.68%
